{"tid":1419663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(和理非) 唔可以浪費勇武嘅成果","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:31:24.000Z","uid":72447,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1eaab9e1c405d0afcc4ce1889df604aa75538c8","tid":1419663,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"去到咁嘅地步<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武義士絕對俾到希望香港人</span></strong><br />\n令到我哋覺得自己有得同政府角力<br />\n既然係咁<br />\n有心為香港好嘅應該趁機爭取治本：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主打雙普選</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n即係訴求都應該 be water，唔好俾政府扣港獨帽子：<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1. 口號避免革命字眼<br />\n2. 繼續仇警但不以仇警心態衝擊<br />\n3. 不被仇恨駕馭</span><br />\n扣到嘅話下場就係大家會被迫割席，白費功夫：雨傘2.0<br />\n<br />\n主打雙普選好處：<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 雙普選切合運動規模<br />\n2. 符合絕大部分香港小市民嘅願望<br />\n3. 符合國際觀感<br />\n4. 可以&ldquo;侵&rdquo;埋泛民亦即&rdquo;侵&ldquo;埋授權佢哋嘅民意</span><br />\n<br />\n但當然<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n小小意見<br />\n不喜任插(溫柔)"},{"pid":"6027116be050e2bc4fd48f8a2917041c95237876","tid":1419663,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:16:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8fee1b8b3704f4e13ab3eab6ba97940f38e95976","tid":1419663,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"994b0228a3ae1cfec484577ea62a40ae468785db","tid":1419663,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7c5d2519727ff7bbdd7d68447b488a5292e4b2f","tid":1419663,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:23:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"95cae7de6b18fb97095d8fab7b13fd5679345862","tid":1419663,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"push"}]}